      !!FU(AdventurerHeroGenerateSkill):Py1/?y3; [Generate skill with adventurer chances.]
    !!en;
    !!if&y8=0/y4=1/y5=0;                         [If right skill is set, left is not and no unupgraded skills. Right skill is left alone, change only left.]
